Interface AbstractCodec

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Base16Codec, Base32Codec, Base64Codec, CSVCodec, ECMACodec, HTMLCodec, JavaCodec, JSONCodec, URLCodec, VariableCodec, XMLCodec, XSICodec
    public interface AbstractCodec
    This wraps various codec (encode/decode) methods used in QDL in a single interface. MetaCodec is instantiated with the correct argument to the constructor and does the right thing.
